VLmLHbRPIbQ.title: Every Episode of Gay Science | Collection 1 | Rob Anderson
VLmLHbRPIbQ.author: Rob Anderson
VLmLHbRPIbQ.description:
Gay Science is a series that asks the question “Why do the gays?” I take queer stereotypes and explain them scientifically with true 100% real science. This is a collection of every episode from the first collection (2020) of Gay Science and Gay Anthropology. In this video we'll answer:

Why do gay men like iced coffee?
Are vers bottoms going extinct?
Why do gay men color their hair in a crisis?
Why can't gay men sit in a chair properly?
Why can't gay men remember each other's names?
Why are gay boys always the female teacher's favorites?
Disney Gays, explained
Plant Gays, explained
Horror Genre Gays, explained
Game Night Lesbians, explained
Why are gay co-workers either best friends or mortal enemies?
